        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "To turn away this anger of God, Hezekiah wishes to make a covenant with the Lord, i.e., to renew the covenant with Jahve by restoring His worship (לבבי עם as in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
